// The Ledger, chapter 4 of 4: THE BUYER. The handoff sours: an unmarked
// military gunship - the AUDITOR - arrives for the box, and the Kestrel
// chooses how the story ends. Two beacons open the branch (OnEnter sets
// `choice`, gauntlet-style): fly the box to Vesh's HANDOFF berth and sell,
// or to the BURN buoy and destroy it. Either way the Auditor must die; the
// ending text differs by `choice`. Branching lives INSIDE the chapter -
// variables do not survive scenario changes (spike 20260716-183104).
//
// Acts: 1 = the choice, 2 = the fight, 3 = done. `choice`: 1 = sold,
// 2 = burned. Player-death Defeat gates act < 3.
[
    Scenario((
        id: "ledger_ch4_the_buyer",
        name: "The Ledger 4: The Buyer",
        description: "Everyone wants the box. Decide who gets it - then survive the decision. Chapter four of The Ledger.",
        cubemap: "dep://base/textures/cubemap.png",
        thumbnail: Some("dep://base/textures/asteroid.png"),
        hidden: true,
        events: [
            (
                name: OnStart,
